智障到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又彈過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69ceb6d82fb7e3518d7e46f8dd910cf1869111d","tid":283102,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:53:23.000Z","msg":"仲彈緊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2200efa0ce03f17cae4d148cf67b53ac5e85982","tid":283102,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/095340_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F095340_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg&h=5d486877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我講緊名隔離紅框呢個時間，邊有可能用咁樣倒數法去顯示俾人睇架<br />\n如果我要睇個幾兩個月前既Post，我點知佢係幾一日出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57db603636367bb12c4a555fad06f1a9155433b5","tid":283102,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:10:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"659437bdc3a0ac66b8375da3f394486f21cda1f0","tid":283102,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:11:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲彈緊呀</span>"},{"pid":"6407cf0d2c63570c10008e5b5860e092af1c275d","tid":283102,"uid":5250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲彈緊呀</span></blockquote><br />\n其他browser有冇事？app有冇事？"},{"pid":"1b4cd9d253a64f13a0313ec9b3f