0Z","msg":"我地已經著手搵緊問題究竟出左係邊到，出事既巴打可唔可以幫手寫返低：<br />\n<br />\n－ OS<br />\n－ browser<br />\n－ 邊個post<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf7559398a4c0d74ffa19f86161126924486185","tid":283102,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地已經著手搵緊問題究竟出左係邊到，出事既巴打可唔可以幫手寫返低：<br />\n<br />\n－ OS<br />\n－ browser<br />\n－ 邊個post<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n電腦Web版<br />\nChorme<br />\n無話邊個Post，轉黎轉去，跟住無端端就彈出黎話咩不能blah blah blah，之後就要重新登人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該搞埋時間呢個問題，真係極之ON9<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/095340_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F095340_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg&h=5d486877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我講緊名隔離紅框呢個時間，邊有可能用咁樣倒數法去顯示俾人睇架<br />\n如果我要睇個幾兩個月前既Post，我點知佢係幾一日出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5503eb45084a064b0a4bbd3374464e83a9c0babf","tid":283102,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"windows web<br />\nchrome<br />\n彈咩驗證失敗,請重新登入之類"},{"pid":"9c45732896db3b5f49ec3118504e43f013c67940","tid":283102,"uid":122859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我地已經著手搵緊問題究竟出左係邊到，出事既巴打可唔可以幫手寫返低：<br />\n<br />\n－ OS<br />\n－ browser<br />\n－ 邊個post<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n電腦Web版<br />\nChorme<br />\n無話邊個Post，轉黎轉去，跟住無端端就彈出黎話咩不能blah blah blah，之後就要重新登人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該搞埋時間呢個問題，真係極之ON9<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/095340_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F095340_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg&h=5d486877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我講緊名隔離紅框呢個時間，邊有可能用咁樣倒數法去顯示俾人睇架<br />\n如果我要睇個幾兩個月前既Post，我點知佢係幾一日出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n關於時間顯示既問題，其實而家已經可以指埋去出tooltip，下一個version會考慮加入設定比人揀預設出邊種時間顯示。"},{"pid":"2a047ef7d59443a9b66ea236dca531e2580d20c4","tid":283102,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w8pg6csb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw8pg6csb&h=18d8a536&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"674214e7775882913cddbc5dd884927414f9e1d9","tid":283102,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我地已經著手搵緊問題究竟出左係邊到，出事既巴打可唔可以幫手寫返低：<br />\n<br />\n－ OS<br />\n－ browser<br />\n－ 邊個post<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n電腦Web版<br />\nChorme<br />\n無話邊個Post，轉黎轉去，跟住無端端就彈出黎話咩不能blah blah blah，之後就要重新登人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該搞埋時間呢個問題，真係極之ON9<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/095340_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F095340_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg&h=5d486877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我講緊名隔離紅框呢個時間，邊有可能用咁樣倒數法去顯示俾人睇架<br />\n如果我要睇個幾兩個月前既Post，我點知佢係幾一日出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n關於時間顯示既問題，其實而家已經可以指埋去出tooltip，下一個version會考慮加入設定比人揀預設出邊種時間顯示。</blockquote><br />\n有得揀就最好啦，因為個次追post想搵番日子同時間都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe3e69839957c5149f1c07d38ed57af06e28e11","tid":283102,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:45:33.000Z","msg":"一個鐘被 logout 3 次"},{"pid":"a8a576df02385ea7d8b7acc0abf39caa3f633798","tid":283102,"uid":75,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:46:48.000Z","msg":"OSX 10.12<br />\nSafari<br />\n無話邊個特定Post，隨時Logout"}]}